It is certified that the work contained in the dissertation titled
``{\sl\@title}'', by {\sl\@author}, Enrolment Number {\sl\@RegNo} has been carried out under 
 our supervision and this work has not been submitted  elsewhere for a degree.
\par
\vspace{3cm}}

